{"name":"Burning Heart","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"This mage throws all caution to the wind to take down his opponents.</p><p> At the beginning of his turn, he may choose to make himself Vulnerable (until the end of his next turn) to apply a –2 penalty to rolls to resist or avoid powers he casts this turn (this does not affect opponent’s rolls to shake the effect off on their turn), and to increase his powers damage by 2.","notes":"Fantasy: Wizards and Mystics page 44","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (any), Strong Willed"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.fantasy-add-ons.6ukxMc1YSDvgXdFd"},"cf":{"id":"temp_w7pvxs6rik","path":"Fantasy Add-Ons","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"iif73aBystNswTq8"}
{"name":"Flexible Caster","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"The hero has mastered how to modify his powers to adapt to various situations.</p><p> Whenever the hero activates a power with at least one Power Modifier selected (with a cost of 1 or higher), the total cost of the power is reduced by 1.","notes":"Fantasy: Tomes and Prayers page 47","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (any), arcane skill d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UeH4lLk57wAOn2HV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.fantasy-add-ons.AJD4YSx8CPXRNe9s"},"cf":{"id":"temp_w7pvxs6rik","path":"Fantasy Add-Ons","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"ioxYgi5wgzigMtgx"}
